  "prompt": "What is the best Instagram followers tracking app?",
  "response": "There are several Instagram followers tracking apps that are popular and highly rated for their features and user experience. Some of the best options include:\n\n1. **Followers Insight for Instagram**: This app provides detailed insights into your followers, including new followers, lost followers, and users who don't follow you back. It also offers engagement metrics and other statistics.\n\n2. **Follower Analyzer for Instagram**: This app lets you analyze your followers and track various metrics such as followers gained and lost, ghost followers, and top likers and commenters. It provides a comprehensive overview of your Instagram activity.\n\n3. **Reports+ for Instagram**: Reports+ is a powerful tool for tracking your Instagram followers and engagement. It offers detailed reports on followers gained and lost, ghost followers, and insights into your most active followers. \n\n4. **Iconosquare**: Iconosquare is a professional social media analytics tool that provides in-depth insights into your Instagram account, including follower growth, engagement rates, and performance metrics. It's suitable for businesses and influencers looking for advanced analytics.\n\n5. **Social Blade**: Social Blade offers analytics for various social media platforms, including Instagram. It provides follower tracking, engagement metrics, and historical data to help you analyze your growth over time.\n\n6. **FollowMeter for Instagram**: FollowMeter provides insights into your followers, including who unfollowed you, who followed you, and who doesn't follow you back. It also offers engagement metrics and other useful statistics.\n\nThese apps vary in their features and pricing, so it's important to consider your specific needs and preferences when choosing the right one for you.",
